            <title><![CDATA[【🌽#玉米叶煮水可辅助降血压# 】玉米叶富含纤维素，可以提取抗氧化的物质。[话筒]专家表示，如果把玉米叶煮水，提取到黄酮类物质，可以疏通血管、促进血液循...]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[【🌽<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E7%8E%89%E7%B1%B3%E5%8F%B6%E7%85%AE%E6%B0%B4%E5%8F%AF%E8%BE%85%E5%8A%A9%E9%99%8D%E8%A1%80%E5%8E%8B%23&amp;extparam=%23%E7%8E%89%E7%B1%B3%E5%8F%B6%E7%85%AE%E6%B0%B4%E5%8F%AF%E8%BE%85%E5%8A%A9%E9%99%8D%E8%A1%80%E5%8E%8B%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#玉米叶煮水可辅助降血压#</span></a> 】玉米叶富含纤维素，可以提取抗氧化的物质。<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[话筒]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/o_huatong-0a3e80b147.png" data-rsshub-image="href" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>专家表示，如果把玉米叶煮水，提取到黄酮类物质，可以疏通血管、促进血液循环，起到辅助降压的作用👇🏻 <a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫唠健康#</span></a>（CCTV生活圈）<a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034:5003532391088200" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_video_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="surl-text">CCTV生活圈的微博视频</span></a> <br clear="both"><div style="clear: both"></div><video controls="controls" poster="https://tvax3.sinaimg.cn/orj480/713e54f1gy1hn00vkaphgj21hc0u0111.jpg" style="width: 100%"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/s21kDhfOlx08cGIIAOy401041200wjUc0E010.mp4?label=mp4_720p&amp;template=1280x720.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1708549978&amp;ssig=hvnaHrxyxj&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/JPe73VCblx08cGIHwsXu01041200gkp40E010.mp4?label=mp4_hd&amp;template=852x480.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1708549978&amp;ssig=G%2FiO7d9Erb&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/IZeZVykqlx08cGIHiFwk01041200aiEe0E010.mp4?label=mp4_ld&amp;template=640x360.25.0&