            <description><![CDATA[[皱眉]生发洗发水，能生发吗？<br><br>真的不能！<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[NO]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/h_buyao-3a904f27f5.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><br><br>头发毛囊生长在头皮的下层组织，而头皮属于表皮层，表皮层下面还有一层真皮层。各类洗发产品是无法渗透到毛囊，从而增加毛发本身的数量的，它顶多能阻止毛囊萎缩，起到延缓脱发的功效。<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[doge]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/d_doge-be7f768d78.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫唠健康#</span></a><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E6%9D%A5%E8%BE%9F%E8%B0%A3%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E6%9D%A5%E8%BE%9F%E8%B0%A3%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫来辟谣#</span></a>（广东疾控） <img style="" src="https://tvax4.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hn03dzptnfg20tz0gvq40.gif" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax2.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hn03dzrs7lj20ic0i9jtd.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax3.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hn03dzpnbpj208s0a4wf6.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br>]]></description>
